_sText: This map took a while to re-do. Yes, I know, it's been re-done like a million times but it's a very popular map, and I had to make a remake for my clan. I've added a lot since the normal. I've taken out the tubes so no more tube camping, I've made realistic roofs and made all doors the correct sizes. I've added as much as I could to increase fps, but still in some spots it's still not the best. I've added some better looking stairs, and added a sun. There is one secret room, but I can't tell where ;) Please don't just say "eh, it's another remake," try it for yourself! We have the map on our server rotation and it's beta, so come check it out: 208.167.247.61:27015 Here's a short video showing more of the map: EDIT: It also includes an awesome radar overview!
